prompt:
Act as an expert content marketer and viral social media strategist with experience creating Instagram posts that reach 100k+ likes. 
Your task is to write a high-engagement Instagram post promoting a new eco-friendly water bottle from the brand “Mosaic”. 
Objectives: - Highlight the sustainability and eco-friendly benefits - Emphasize the bottle’s unique styles and aesthetic designs 
- Make the product feel trendy, premium, and lifestyle-oriented - Encourage engagement (likes, saves, and comments)
Target audience: Gen Z and young adults who care about sustainability, aesthetics, and lifestyle products.
Tone: Trendy, aspirational, relatable, and Instagram-friendly.
Post structure: 1. A strong scroll-stopping hook in the first line
2. Short engaging caption explaining the benefits
3. Highlight 4–6 key benefits of the eco-friendly bottle 
4. Mention the stylish designs and lifestyle appeal
5. End with a call-to-action encouraging engagement
6. Include 12–15 high-performing hashtags for sustainability, lifestyle, and eco-friendly products
7. Add a few relevant emojis to make the post visually engaging
Important: - Make the caption optimized for Instagram engagement - Keep sentences short and punchy - Make it feel authentic and not overly promotional - Ensure the caption has strong viral potential (100k+ likes level content)
used CHATGPT to get desired output

